This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Science sub-category of Network and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) as it deals with mobile edge caching and recommendation systems. It could also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as it focuses on YouTube video recommendations. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is another possible sub-category as the paper discusses how to leverage information provided by the recommendation system. Data Structures (cs.DS) could also be a relevant sub-category as the paper proposes an approach for caching optimization. Finally, Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) could be a relevant sub-category as the paper deals with recommendation systems and their impact on network efficiency.
